tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotify.name: tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotify
tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotify.description: A notification sent when a user attempts to log into the device but fails to authenticate.

tptNgfwUserAuthLockedAccountNotify.name: tptNgfwUserAuthLockedAccountNotify
tptNgfwUserAuthLockedAccountNotify.description: A notification sent when a user account is locked after exceeding the allowed number of login attempts.

tptNgfwUserAuthLockedIpNotify.name: tptNgfwUserAuthLockedIpNotify
tptNgfwUserAuthLockedIpNotify.description: A notification sent when too many failed login attempts occur from the same source IP address.

tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotifyReason.name: tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotifyReason
tptNgfwUserAuthFailNotifyReason.description: The reason for the user authentication failure.

tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddrType.name: tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddrType
tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddrType.description: The type of IP address of the source IP address object.

tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddr.name: tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddr
tptNgfwUserAuthSrcIpAddr.description: The device IP from where the user attempted to authenticate.

tptNgfwUserAuthNotifySource.name: tptNgfwUserAuthNotifySource
tptNgfwUserAuthNotifySource.description: The source or interface (SSH, LSM, SMS, Console) used to make an authentication attempt.

tptNgfwUserAuthLockedTime.name: tptNgfwUserAuthLockedTime
tptNgfwUserAuthLockedTime.description: The time a user account or IP address was locked.

tptNgfwUserGroup.name: tptNgfwUserGroup
tptNgfwUserGroup.description: User group containing objects related to user stats.
